data.text: The donut charts show the demographic breakdown of customers. The arrows indicate if the figures have increased (green) or decreased (red) compared the previous month.
In April 2022, the overall demographics has remained unchanged compared to previous month. There are significant changes in Gender.
The multi-line graph shows the trend of patrons based on their age over time in April, 2022.

The highest number of patrons from a single age group was on th April with 3900 from the Elderly age group. The lowest number of patrons from a single age group was on th April with 50 from the Young Adults age group.
